      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "thanks. i tried to check the caliper and it seems like it's moving okay, but the noise is still super annoying and it happens almost every time i slow down. is there any way to tell if the noise is coming specifically from a sensor or if it's something else deeper in the assembly?",
